data.description: Check out this ranch style home in a desired west end neighborhood! 4142 Sedgwick features an excellent floor plan! The vaulted ceiling makes the home feel so spacious! 2 bedrooms up, 1 bathroom and wonderful open living space. Downstairs you will find a huge family room with built in theatre room for all of the movie fun you can imagine, 2 more bedrooms and a bathroom. The quaint backyard has a concrete patio that could easily be turned into a little oasis. Another concrete pad that could be a great spot for a hot tub, fire pit or raised flower beds. Come and make this home yours today!
